	<description>
		<p>Serial Studio lets you see real-time data from microcontrollers and connected devices. It's perfect for visualizing sensor readings, telemetry, and debugging data from serial ports, Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE), and TCP/UDP sources.</p>
		<p>Whether you're a student, hobbyist, or engineer, Serial Studio helps you understand what's happening inside your hardware.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Cross-platform: Native support for Windows, macOS, and Linux.</li>
      <li>CSV export: Save incoming data for offline analysis or processing.</li>
      <li>Multiple inputs: Connect via serial, BLE, MQTT, or TCP/UDP.</li>
      <li>Custom dashboards: Build interfaces with visual widgets in the Project Editor.</li>
      <li>Advanced decoding: Use JavaScript to parse raw or binary data streams.</li>
		</ul>
		<p>For commercial use and advanced features like MQTT, XY plots, and 3D views, a Pro license is available.</p>
	</description>
